  body
    .container
      h1 LFUCG Data Endpoints
      p Data enpoints for integration with LFUCG vendors. Base URL is https://lfucg-data.herokuapp.com.
      .panel
        h2 /api/v1/police
        p Returns police cases that occured on or after a supplied date.
        h3 Required Query Parameters
        p apikey | string | Valid API Key string supplied by LFUCG
        p date | date | ex. 05-15-2017
        h3 Example
        p
          | Return police cases on or after May 11, 2017.
        p https://lfucg-data.herokuapp.com/api/v1/police?apikey=APIKEY&date=05-11-2017
      .panel
        h2 /api/v1/waterservice
        p Returns water service records with a charge date or adjustment date on or after the supplied date.
        h3 Required Query Parameters
        p apikey | string | Valid API Key string supplied by LFUCG
        p date | date | ex. 05-15-2017
        h3 Example
        p
          | Return water service records with a with a charge date or adjustment date on or after April 15, 2017. 
        p https://lfucg-data.herokuapp.com/api/v1/waterservice?apikey=APIKEY&date=04-15-2017
